<h2>balance: Visualize Balances of Compositional Data</h2>
<p>Balances have become a cornerstone of compositional data analysis. However,
 conceptualizing balances is difficult, especially for high-dimensional data. Most often,
 investigators visualize balances with "balance dendrograms". However, this visualization
 tool does not scale well for large data. This package provides an alternative scheme for
 visualizing balances, described in [Quinn (2018) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.12688%2Ff1000research.15858.1">doi:10.12688/f1000research.15858.1</a>&gt;].
 This package also provides a method for principal balance analysis.</p>
